{"tid":565852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依家啲細路仔真係好奀皮……","createTime":"2018-02-19T11:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T11:24:51.000Z","uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1f5735077e588dd4737b826e366a3b3ff44da198","tid":565852,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://viu.tv/encore/super-daddy#super-daddye1hok-wooi-laang-jing-ching-sui\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2Fencore%2Fsuper-daddy%23super-daddye1hok-wooi-laang-jing-ching-sui&d=vmKD4W8mTms%2Fq90gnFo94jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4a04914d\" target=\"_blank\">http://viu.tv/encore/super-daddy#super-daddye1hok-wooi-laang-jing-ching-sui</a><br />\n過咗一個月，我諗大家都會冷靜啲<br />\n佢提倡嘅管教係唔使鬧唔使打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢集個家庭個細路仔成日會打人，但係用咗佢啲方法之後呢，個細路嘅情況有所改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗成套方法嘅重點係首先要建立一個良好嘅親子關係，然後先去講管教。而管教係需要父母嘅耐性同堅持。耐性嘅意思係你唔可能期望個細路仔嘅問題會一下子冇咗，佢哋係需要慢慢去學習，當佢有進步嘅時候，就算呢個進步係好少，都要比鼓勵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n堅持就係唔好用用下啲方法就心軟，要貫徹實行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外一樣都好重要，就係所有照顧者要對管教方法有共識，唔係根本就會實行唔到啲技巧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁佢啲方法唔一定對個個細路都work，咁就要再搵其他途徑學習其他方法，就好似當打同流唔work果陣，就要嘗試其他方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a353f22f9cccbb139eeb0b97843dc184738dd01c","tid":565852,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"同埋我都覺得呢集個阿媽太soft ，抱個細路仔去張凳度楚到底有幾暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}